
[1]specify

   SPEC'IFY, v.t. To mention or name, as a particular thing; to designate
   in words so as to distinguish a thing from every other; as, to specify
   the uses of a plant; to specify the articles one wants to purchase. He
   has there given us an exact geography of Greece, where the countries
   and the uses of their soils are specified.
